column2: NCASA2    <- ggplot(SANTIAGO,aes(x = cluster2,y = NCASA))    + geom_boxplot() + labs(title = "Numero de casas  por zona"                          , x = "Cluster", y = "Cantidad")   + geom_hline(aes(yintercept = mean(NCASA))   ,linetype="dotted",size=1.5,color="deeppink1")
